description: From the very basic topics that lead to the creation of World Wide Web to being able to write Professional Level JQuery Scripts, this course will teach you everything from HTML5, CSS, Java Script, JQuery and a bit of Ajax. We have a project at the end after we complete all the lectures and some Bonus classes included relating to the next generation of World Wide Web.
title: HTML5, Java Script, DOM, JQuery & Ajax Basic to Intermediate
